<SYNC Start=847408><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=848714><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah?
<SYNC Start=850079><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=852618><P Class=ENCC>
