<SYNC Start=935935><P Class=ENCC>
No, best time ever.
<SYNC Start=938130><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=939805><P Class=ENCC>
Yeah. You rock my world.
<SYNC Start=942706><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
